  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the clinical investigation is to assess the clinical and subjective
      performance of three novel multipurpose disinfecting solutions (MPDS) in daily wear with two
      silicone hydrogel contact lenses (Lotrafilcon B and Comfilcon A).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
